name: women we do not see.
description:
Women who are neither beautiful nor famous ... who are born in the slums and live in the shadows of kitchens and die in Corners of houses. Women who born in rural areas out of sights. Their beauty is forgotten in the backyard as their dreams fade away under the wrinkles of their faces and the calluses of their hands. Real women… women who we do not see.
From the collection of "People we do not see"
